            "stanza_text": "Faisant sonner leur gaieté franche\nDans leur beau rire à plein gosier,\nIls massacrent le cerisier,\nEt chacun emporte sa branche."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 2,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 5,
                    "line_text": "Mais quelle branche ! longue et large,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 6,
                    "line_text": "Toute foisonnante de fruit,",
